ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2005-2006
PrecisAppointment of RICK CASSON of Lethbridge, Alberta, as Chairman of the Canadian Section of the Canada-United States Permanent Joint Board on Defence in the place of Judi Longfield; and request that RICK CASSON, Member of Parliament for the electoral district of Lethbridge, do undertake such travel as may be necessary for the purposes of the above appointment.
